(u'www.hindimehelp.com', u'/rohit-mewada-life-secrets/', u'Rohit Mewada ki Life ke Secrets jo Kisi ko Nahi Pata | Hindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHSearchHindi Me HelpHomeBloggingBloggerWordPressBloggingSEOGuest PostsSocial MediaFacebookTwitterYouTubeGoogleWhatsappSocial NetworkInternetImportant WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHHomeHindi Me HelpRohit Mewada ki Life ke Secrets jo Kisi ko Nahi PataHindi Me HelpRohit Mewada ki Life ke Secrets jo Kisi ko Nahi PataBy Rohit Mewada - May 27, 2017171Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestHello Friends, Aaj Date hai 27/05/2017 yani ki mera Bday.. isliye ye din mere liye Special to hai ki, par jo log mujse chate hai , Muje pasand karte hai, jo muje support karte hai unki baja se ye din mere liye or bhi jada Special Ban gaya hai.Mere Bhut se Friends hai jo mere ware me jaanna chate hai or unke bhut se sabal bhi hai jinka jabab abhi tak kisi ko nahi pata hai, par aaj me mere wo sare raaj open karne wala hu.. Kuch bate to aesi hai jo abhi tak mere aalawa kisi or ko nahi pata hai.Sabse Phele Baat karte hai me phele kis type ka banda tha, kya karta tha, kya soch thi meri or kya karna chata tha wo jaan lete hai uske baad jo Sabal hai unke jabab diye jayege.Meri Life ke Top SecretMe ek aese kism ka ladka tha, jo andar hi andar bhut kuch sochta tha, or andar kya chal raha hai wo kisi se share bhi nahi karta tha.. q ki muje kahi na kahi aesa lagta tha ki me agar kisi se share karuga to wo samjega nahi or sayad mera majak bhi udaye.School Time me 8th class tak to kuch extra nahi kiya.. Normal School se ghar, TV, Khana-Pina, Sona wass ye hi sab normal chalta raha.8th Class me pheli war mene Computer ko use kiya School me, uss time to usko chalu kaise karna hai ya band kaise karna hai iss baat ne hi pasine chuda diye the.. par dhire dhire thoda knowledge bada..Ab Internet bhikuch chij hoti hai, jiska use karke ham kuch bhi dekh sakte hai, kuch bhi search kar sakte hai aesa pata chala.. to wass ab isme thoda interest jag gaya.Ek war mere ek Friend ne online Map par uske ghar ka naksha dikhaya, par ye usne kaise kiya ye usne nahi bataya.. Wass Fir kya tha Net Cafe ke chakkar lagna chalu huee, or Internet par pata nahi kya kya search karte, Game khelte.. Fir aese hi dhire dhire bhut si chijo ke ware me pata chala.. or WikiMapia ek site hai jispar ham apna Map set kar sakte hai ye bhi pata chala..Fir Kya tha Map set karke, mere uss friend ko bataya jo nahi bata raha tha ki usne kaise kiya.. wass ye sab chal raha tha..Yaha par jo sabse Interesting baat thi wo ye, ki Jab bhi Net Cafe jate the to wo hamara Naam or Mobile Number puchte the.. aese hi security propose ke liye..

2.Brute Force Attack Se Password Hack Kaise Kare Mostly sabhi password is method se koi ek hacker tod sakta hai,Ab aap soch rahe honge ki maine bola tha ki agar aap sahi se spacial character use karte hai to koi bhi password nhi tod payega.To dosto pura sentence padhiye maine sirf ye kaha ki sabhi password bruteforce attack se toot sakte hai lekin kitni der me tootenge ye nhi bataya ,to aapko bata du ki agar aapke passowrd me simple character hai ,numbers hai albhabat hai to bruteforce attack se asani se aapka passowrd crack kar liya jayega lekin isme bhi kam se kam 1 ghante ka time lagega ,aur socho agar aapka passowrd strong hai usme spacial character jaise @#$%^& ka use hua hai to brute force attack se ye bhi password toot jayega lekin lagbhag 200 years me ,to aap samjh gaye honge ki strong password ko tod pana nearly impossible hai.

aaj me aapko HindiMeHelp ke dusre guest post me Windows 10 me chalne wale background update yani ki Windows auto update ko kaise off kiya jaata hai iske bare me batane wala hu.Windows 7 me chalne wale auto updates ko hum asaani se off kar sakte the lekin Windows 10 me aisa nahi hai, windows 10 me windows update ko off karne ka aisa kuch option diya hi nahi hai jisse hum auto update rok sake.Windows update hone par humare bahut sara data teji se khatam hota hai.Windows Auto Update me 3 trha se Data barbad hota hai1: Sabse pahala karan ye hai ki windows 10 me Microsoft ne kuch changes kiye hai ki pahale hum apne marji update install kar sakte the lekin ab Microsoft ne windows 10 me aisa kuch kar diya ki hum updates ko rok nahi sakte vo apne aap ho jaygi aur is tarah se apna data apne aap use ho jaata hai aur aapko pata bhi nahi chalta.2: Aur dusra karan ye hai Microsoft ne windows 10 me ek aur changes kiye hai isme aapki windows 10 me jab aap koi update karte hai uski data aapke computer me internet ke jariye use upload karte rahte hai taki dure ki update fast ho taki Microsoft ki jo server hai uspar jada load na pade.3: Data waste ka tisra karan ye hai ki Microsoft ne windows 10 me one drive ko dala hai aur ye aapke data ko online backup karti hai, lekin isme aapki internet data waste hoti hai.

Best WordPress Theme use kareYaha mera Best WordPress theme se matlab hai ek badiya theame, ab wo paid ho ya free ho usse koi fark nahi padta wass aap jaha se bhi theme le wo secure ho.Yaha sabse jada log galti karte hai, lagbhag 80% log wo ye ki jo Paid Theme hai, unka crack theme version use karte hai, jo bhut badi galti hai.jo crack theme use karte hai wo ek trha se aesa kar rahe hai ki ek GUN ko load karke apne sar par lagali or samne wale se khe rahe hai (jo unko marna hi chata hai) ki uska trigger daba do, khene ka matlab khud marne ki puri teyari karli.Aap khud socho koi bhi jo chij paise me milti hai wo free me q dega, or sabse main baat agar koi crack theme use karta hai to uski site sirf hack hone ka khatra nahi iske aalawa bhi bhut nuksan hai.Crack theme use karne se jo hosting bandwidth hai wo bhut jada use hoti hai jiske karan hosting account suspend ho sakta hai or jo developer hote hai wo bhi itni mhenat karte hai theme ko banane me to wo bhi kisi ko unki mhenat free me use to karne dege nahi, wo aesi script bhi use karte hai jiske karan aapki site google me penalize (google se remove) bhi ho sakti hai.mene bhut logo ko dekha jo paise nahi hone ke karan crack theme use karte hai, me aapko bata du, ek war crack theme install karne ke baad wo aasani se remove nahi hoti hai, uske kuch harmful files ko chor hi deti hai site me, to kabhi main site me crack theme install karke bhi naa dekhe.Hindi Me Help par Newspaper theme hai, agar aapko ye pasand hai to aap yaha se kharid sakte hai.#14: Badiya Plugin use kareYe Point bhi same upar wale point ki trha hai, matlab naa aapko Crack plugin use karni hai or naa aesi jagha se download karna hai jo trusted naa ho.Kisi bhi plugin ko install karne se phele uski rating or uski downloads bhi jarur check kare, jisse aapko andaja lag jayega wo plugin badiya hai ya nahi.

Jab aapko ye pata chal jaye ki aapka Passion kya hai to uske baad apne aap se ye kuch sabal puche, jisse aapko clear ho jayega ki haa ye hi aapka passion hai. Aapko jo Pasand hai wo Q Pasand hai? Mene kuch Time phele bataya tha Whatsapp ke iss update [&#8230;] The post Whatsapp Send Kiya Message ko Recall Kaise kare [Delete for Everyone] appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Whatsapp ka Sabse Bada Update or sabse jada jiski Demand thi wo Update aa chuka hai, Whatsapp Message ko Recall (DELETE FOR EVERYONE) karne ka jisme ham Galti se send huee Message ko delete kar sakte hai jisko send huaa hai uske Mobile se bhi. Mene kuch Time phele bataya tha Whatsapp ke iss update ke ware me jo ab aa chuka hai. Whatsapp ke Iss Feature ka use karne ke liye aapko sabse phele whatsapp ko update karna hoga.. Update Whatsapp ye jo update hai wo whatsapp version 2.17.395 ya usse upar ke version me hai. Whatsapp Update karne ke baad aap kisi ko bhi koi message send kare.. uske baad jab aap uss message ko delete karege to ek option or aayegaDELETE FOR EVERYONEka, jisko select karke se message har jagha se delete ho jayega.. jisko send kiya hai unke mobile se bhi. Note: ye jo Option hai message ko har jagha se delete karne ka wo ham sirf 7 minute tak aata hai, uske baad send kiye message ko delete nahi kar sakte. Message delete karne ke baad uss message ki jagha You Delete this message likha huaa aayega or jisko wo message send kiya tha waha This message was deleted likha huaa aayega. To ab jo Galti se jo galti ho jati thi, jisme kisi or ka message or kisi ko send ho jata tha ab wo nahi hoga.. Q ki ab hame hamari Galti sudharne ke liye 7 minutes ka Time bhi milega.

hote hai, to agar aapko wo dono pata ho ki isme kya faide hai or kya nuksan hai to fir aap aasani se deside kar sakte hai ki aapko kya karna hai.Aapko ye bhi sochna padega ki agar aap blogging me apna career banane me agar fail ho gaye to fir aapke hath me kya rahega or aapke ek fesle se aapki puri life kesi jayegi wo depend karti hai to aap ye fesla aap aasani se naa le or iske liye achi se soche.. me abhi kuch bate batane wala hu unke ware me jarur soche.Blogging me Career Banane se phele jane ye Bate1: Aapka koi Bose Nahi RahegaAgar aap Blogging karte hai ya koi bhi aesa kaam karte hai jisme aapka koi bose nahi rahega to aapko faida ye hai ki aap jab chahe kaam kar sakte hai or aapko kisi se dab kar rhene ki bhi jarurat nahi hogi, par iske sath ek nuksan bhi hai agar aap blogging karte hai to wo ye ki aapko kisi ka dar nahi rhega ki agar mera ye kaam nahi huaa to koi muje datega isse hoga ye.. ho sakta hai aap aapna kaam time par naa kare jisse aapko blogging me bada nuksan ho sakta hai or blogging me fail hone ka karan bhi ye ban sakta hai.To agar aap blogging me apna career banana chate hai top sabse important hai ki aapka pane upar itna control ho ki aap apna kaam time par sahi tarike se kar sake bina kisi ke dabab ke bina..2: Time ki koi Boundary NahiBlogging karne ka ek faida ye haiki aapko time ki koi boundary nahi rahegi jese job me rheti hai ki aapko itni baja se itni baje tak kaam karna hai, aap jab chahe jab aapna blogging ka kaam kar sakte hai par yaha bhi ek nuksan hai wo ye ki job me fix time hota hai ki itne time kaam karna hai par blogging me aapko extra time bhi dena hoga..khene ka matlab hai agar aap job karte hai to aapko 8 ghante kaam karna hai par agar aap blogging karte hai ya koi bhi Business karte hai to aapko 24 ghante apna dimag apne kaam ko dena hoga, haa aap apne dusre kamo ke liye bhi usme se time nikal sakte hai par aap yaha ye nahi soch sakte ki aap free ho or aapke pass ab bhut jada time hai.3: Jagha ki koi Problem nahiAgar aap kahi job karte hai to aapko office jana padta hai par agar aap blogging karte hai to aap kahi se bhi apna blogging kaa kaam kar sakte hai.
aur ha waise bloggers khoob ak dusare ki post ko copy karte rahte hai.

Agar aapne abhi tak Apne Mobile Number me aadhaar Number ko Verify nahi karaya hai [&#8230;] The post Mobile Number Me Call karke Aadhaar Card Number Verify kare appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Hello Every one, Agar aap ek Indian hai to shidhi si baat hai aapka Aadhaar Card to hoga hi, or aapko pata ho hoga Government ka aadesh ke aanusar har ek mobile number se aadhaar number link hona jaruri hai. Agar aapne abhi tak Apne Mobile Number me aadhaar Number ko Verify nahi karaya hai to aapke pass usse sambandit call or message bhi jarur aate hoge. to chaliye jaan lete hai kaise Aadhaar Number ko Mobile number se link karte hai. Aadhaar ko mobile number se verify karne ka ek tarika to ye hai ki ham kisi dukandar ke pass jaye jo Aadhaar number ko mobile se verify karta ho, or usko kuch paise dekar verify kara le.. par ek or Tarika bhi hai Aadhaar link kare Mobile Number se [IVRS Method] Iss tarike se Mobile number me aadhaar number verify karne ke liye hame ek number hai uspar call karna hai, or usme jo steps batai jaye unko follow karna hai. Step 1: Apne Mobile se Call kare 14546 par. Call 14546 Step 2: Ab ek computer generated aabaj aayegi, jisme hame apni language select karne ko kaha jayega.

| SEO Kaise karte hai Site Rank Karane ke liye" href="https://www.hindimehelp.com/seo-kya-hai/">SEO Kya hai On-Page SEO Keyword Kya Hota Hai Agar aapko upar diye Topic ke ware me jankari hai to aap teyar hai Yoast plugin ka sahi tarike se use karne ke liye. Yoast Plugin Kya hai ? Yoast WordPress plugin hai, jisme SEO ki settings hoti hai.. iski madad se post ka SEO analyse kiya ja sakta hai focus keyword set karke. Simple ham khe sakte hai Yoast plugin hame On Page SEO karne me help karti hai, or kahi kuch gadwad hoti hai to uske ware me batati hai. Note: Agar aapka Blog Blogger par hai, fir bhi aap iss post ko pura read kare, Q ki bhale aap yoast plugin use naa kare par jo point hai wo pure karna jaruri hai SEO ke liye. Yoast Green Signal Kya hai: WordPress me post likhte time niche ek box aata hai yoast plugin ka, jisme ham focus keyword daal kar post ka on page SEO check kar sakte hai, jisme hame pata chalta hai ki SEO me kaha kya kami hai. *Jab Post likhte hai to Yoast ke kuch point to green aasni se ho jate hai , par kuch aese point bhi hote hai jo green nahi ho pate, to uska kya karana hai or kaise iski madad se SEO Friendly post likhe chailye dekhte hai. Green All Yoast Plugin Signal Sabhi point ko detail me batane se phele me aapko bata du, jo bhi point hai wo kisi trna program kiye gaye hai.. to ho sakta hai aap sahi kare fir bhi kuch point green naa ho.

WebsiteToolsInternetMake MoneyMotivationalMoreComputerMobileFestivalHMHHomeYouTubeYoutube Partner Program 4,000 hour/1,000 subscriber Limit Update in HindiYouTubeYoutube Partner Program 4,000 hour/1,000 subscriber Limit Update in HindiBy Rohit Mewada - January 17, 201852Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestYoutube jo ki ek aesa platform hai yaha koi bhi apne Video upload karke duniya se share kar sakta hai, or Video ko monetize karke usse paise bhi kama sakta hai.Youtube se Paise kaise kamaye or kaise Channel ko monetize kare uske ware me phele hi bata chuka hu, agar aap new hai to aap yaha dekh sakte hai.Youtube se apniYoutube Partner Program (YPP) me ek bada update kiya hai jisse jo chote channel hai wo ab paise nahi kama payege, abhi me ussi update ke ware me batane wala hu.. ki wo kya hai or uski kya limits hai.Youtube ne kuch time phele ek update kiya tha, jisme channel ke total views 10,000 hoge, uske baad hi monetize enable hoga.. lekin ab thoda usse bhi muskil hone wala hai.Youtube Partner Program Update Kya haiYoutube Channel ko monetize chalu karne ke liye Channel ke pichle 12 mahino me 4,000 hours watch time hona jaruri hai or uske sath 1,000 subscriber bhi.Ye aap Youtube Official Blog par bhi read kar sakte hai.Starting me monetize enable karne ke liye total 10,000 views to chaiye hi, par uske sath sath ab 4000 Hours/1000 subscriber bhi hona jaruri hai pichle 12 mahino me.Ye jo Update hai wo 20 February 2018 se apply ho jayega..Agar aapki channel new hai, ya aap New Channel banane ka soch rahe hai jispar monetize enable nahi hai to aapko ye limit puri karni hogi, uske baad hi monetize on hoga..Agar aapki channel par monetize on hai, par aapki channel par jada views nahi aate, or aapki channel par pichle ek saal me 4000 hours watch time se kam hai or 1000 subscriber se kam bade hai to aapka monetize bhi disable ho jayega.Jese hi jo limit hai wo puri hoti hai, monetize ke liye apply kar sakte hai..Agar aapka phele monetize on tha, par new limit ke karan disable hua hai to aap badiya video dale or jese hi aapki limit puri ho.. aap suspend hone ke ek mahine baad double se apply kar sakte hai.Youtube ka khena hai, ye update unhone youtube creators ke liye hi kiya hai, taki jo galat kaam karte hai wo dur rahe.Youtube par 90% aesi channels hai jinki one year ki earning 100$ se kam hai ya ek mahine me 2$ hoti hai, aesi channel ab monetize nahi hopayegi.At Last:Mere hisab se to ye update bhut badiya hai, q ki agar aese channel hai jo 100$ se kam kamate the ek saal me.. to agar kisi ki aesi channel hai to wo ab earning ko naa dekhte huee badiya video dalege, or fir jada views aayege to earning bhi jada hogi.Aapko Kya lagta hai Youtube Partner Program ka ye update acha hai ya bura, or isse aapke youtube channel par kya aasar padha wo bhi share kare.. or agar isse sambandit koi sabal ho to aap wo bhi jarur puche.TAGSyoutubeFacebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestPrevious articleSEO Kya hai ?
But iske liye word processing, desktop publishing, languages, etc.

Sirf Comment nahi Ache Comment Bhut Log Comment sirf Backlink ke liye karte hai, agar aap bhi unme se hai to aap in points ko jarur follow kare.. nahi to aapke comment spam khelayege.. or jis maksad se aapne comment kiya hai uska sahi result aapko nahi milega.Har Chij ke kuch Rules hote hai agar ham unko Follow karke kaam kare to Thoda time jarur lagta hai par usse jo hae faida milta hai wo bhi acha hi hota hai.. or kisi chij ka nuksan nahi hota..Comment karte samay bhi Kuch bate hai jinko agar diyan me rakh kar comment kare kisi bhi Blog par to uska Faida hame jarur milta haiComment Karte Samye Rakhe In Bato ka DiyanSabse Phele Post ko Pade achi se.Purane Comment Pade.Agar kisi Comment ka Jabab aapko pata hai to reply bhi kare.Comment Post ke smband me hi kare.Spam Comment naa kare.Chote Comment karne ka bhi koi faida nahi hai.Galat sabdo ka bilkul istmal naa kare.Ek hi Comment bar bar naa kare.Badiya Comment karnePar Rakhe in Bato ko Diyan meComment karte samay sabse phele to hamara pura focus ussi par hona chaiye.. baki aap Aage Pad kar jaan lijiye..#1 Post ko Puri Padne ke baad Comment kareAgar aap kisi Post par Comment kar rahe hai to Sabse Phele post ko pade, Q ki usse aapko post me kya hai ye pata chal jayega or Fir aap apne Vichar comment me share kar sakte ho..Jese aapko ye post kesi lagi.Post me Kya Acha Laga.Post me kya acha nahi laga.Post me kya galat hai.agar koi jankari di gai hai post me to usse sambandit sabal puchne me bhi help milegi post padne ke baad.#2 Purane Comment ko Pade apna Comment karne ke pheleYe Process bhi jaruri hai, Q ki agar aap jo comment kar rahe ho jo phele se hai to aapke comment ko value nahi di jayegi.. Purane comment ko padne ke baad aapko acha Idea bhi mil jayega ki aesa comment kare jo dusre comment karne walo ko bhi impress kare.#3 Galat Sabdo ka bilkul Istmal Naa KareYe batane ki jarurat nahi hai ki Q galat sabdo ka istmal naa kare comment ya kahi bhi.. Galat chij galat hi hoti hai or wo kisi ko pasand nahi aati hai..#4 Dusre Comment ka Reply kareJis Topic par Post hai agar aapko uska knowlage hai aapko or agar koi usse sambandit sabal comment me karta hai to aap uska reply karke uski help kar sakte ho.. isse aapki ek badiya Image ban jayegi ki aapko bhi iska acha knowlage hai.Comment ke Link add karne ka naa soche isse aap spam ki category me aa jayege.#5 Spam Comment Naa KareSpam ka matlab Farji.. Farji comment bhi karte hai bhut log or sochte hai isse blog ki traffic bad jayegi par hota uska bilkul ulta hai.. Jo Blog ka owner hai wo hi delete kar dega or agar nahi karta hai to uske blog ko uska nuksan bhugtna padega..Spam Comment is trha ke hote hai Kisi Referal link ko share karnaKisi Galat site ki link ko share karnaEk hi Comment bar bar har post par karnaInke aalawa bhi farji comment ho sakte hai jo dekhte hi samaj aa jate hai..#6 Chote Comment Nahi Nahi kareComment kar rahe hai to jo comment hai uski ek alag hi value honi chaiye aesa nahi, ki comment kar rahe hai to chota mota kuch bhi likh kar comment kar diya.. usse bhi koi faida nahi..Kuch udharan comments keThank youNice PostHelp MeGreat ArticleMe aapki har post padta huAgar koi Is Trha ke comment karte hai to ho sakta hai wo jisne post dali hai usko impress karde par usse jada or koi faida nahi hai.#7 Comment Post ke Smbandit kareBhut log ye galti karte hai.. Agar koi sabal hai kisi post se sambandit to usse post me kare usse ye faida hoga ki aapko uska jabab sahi tarike se milega or agar jo sabal aapka hai wo or kisi ka bhi hoga to usko bhi jabab mil jayega..Dusri post me kisi dusri post se sambandit comment karne me sabko confusion hota hai or samaj nahi aata hai is comment ka matlab kya hai..#8 Comment me Link add nahi karebhut log Comment karte hi is liye hai ki unki link share kar sake.. par aesa karne se faide se jada nuksan hai.. Aapne Notice kiya ho sayad ki jo ache or popular blog hai to apne comment me link allow nhi karte or aese comment ko turant delete kar dete hai..Link Share karne se ek nuksan ye bhi hai ki isse pata chal jata hai ki aapke blog par visitor kam hai matlab aapke blog me quality nahi hai.. to q koi aapki link par click karke aapke blog par jaye..Link Share kar sakte hai par sirf jab jab uski bhut jarurat ho or jaruri nahi wo aapke blog ki hi link ho.. Jo aap comment kar rahe hai or agar aap usse sambandit kuch dikhana chate hai to link ka use kar sakte hai..Me Link add karke apne Comment ki value badaoga uska Example: Jese Maanlo kisi post me Google SERP ke bare me bataya gaya hai.. or muje usme kuch kami lage.. Google ka koi New Update aaya to me Comment me bataoga ki aapki jankari sahi hai par ye thodi purani hai.. Google ke new update me kuch change kiye hai.. fir me Google ka jo official Blog hai uski link de duga jaha muje new jankari ka pata chala.. isse mere comment ko value di jayegi or jo bhi us comment ko padege wo bhi sochege ki isko acha knowlage hai.. or mere naam ke sath apni website blog me website ki link di hogi to uspar click karke meri website par bhi aayege..#9 Ek Hi Comment Bar Bar Nahi kareEk hi comment bar bar karne se bhi koi faida nahi hai, isse sirf ye sabit hoga ki ye sirf spam comment hai or iske pas or kuch likhne ko nahi hai..To Dosto Ye Kuch Tips thi ek badiya comment karne ke liye, Ummid hai aapko isse jarur kuch sikhne ko mila hoga.. or me Intjar karuga aapke Badiya Comments ka Is Post par ki aapko ye post kesi lagi or agar aapke pass bhi koi or point hai jo Comment karte samay diyan me rakhna chaiye to wo bhi jarur bataye..

*Aesa to bilkul naa soche ki mera blog hai to me dusre blog par q jao Mistake 15:Guest Post Na Karna : Agar aapko Apne Blog ki ranking improve karni hai Backlink ki madad se or aap chate hai jada logo tak aapke Blog ki jankari poche to uska sabse sahi or best tarika hai Guest Posting.Guest Post karne ke kya faide hai wo aap yaha read kar sakte hai, or agar aap HMH.pe Guest post karna chate hai to wo bhi kar sakte hai.Mistake 16:Hatkar Post na likhna: Agar aap koi post kar rahe hai jo phele se hai to ek trha se aap apna time barbad kar rahe hai, agar aap chate hai ki aap jo post likhe uski mhenat ka fal aapko mile to aapko kuch hatke hi karna padega jo phele se na ho..Jab bhi post likhe to search karke bhi dekhe or agar phele se uske ware me post hai to usse achi or badiya tarike se post likhe taki aapki post kaam ki rahe, nahi to same post to phele se hai to koi aapke blog par koi q aayega or aese me Google bhi aapke blog ko Top par q dikhayega.Mistake 17:Dusre blog par comment na karna : Agar aap Dusre Blog ki post to read karte hai or kabhi unpar comment nahi karte to bhi ek trha se galti kar rahe hai, Q ki comment karne se Backlink to milta hi hai par agar aap kuch badiya comment karte ho to uske site owner se bhi aapke ache relation ban jayege, jisse indirectly faida aapko hi hai.Sirf Comment naa kare, Badiya Comment kare or Badiya Comment kaise karte hai uski tips yaha share ki gai hai.Mistake 18:Comment ka reply na karna : apne blog par aaye huye comment ( swalo ) ka jawab nahi dene se blogger ki image par galat effect padta hai.

Hacking Kya Hai-(What Is Hacking) Hacking Ek aisa tarika hai jise ham Internet ki banayi security system ko todke usme apne hisaab se kuch bhi galat ya sahi changes kar sakte hai.Jaise ki system ko access karna matlab ke system ko apne kabu me karke usme viewing,editing,data copying,information ko copy karna,hidden file changes etc.Koi hacker jab hacking karta hai tab uska maksad kuch alag hi karne ka hota hai.Ham hackers ke maksad ko nahi jaan sakte sab hackers ka alag-alag maksad hota hai.Hacker Matlab ke koi banda system ke sath judkar system ke sath kuch aisi harkate karta hai jisse system ko nuksaan hota hai,aise insaan ko Hacker kaha jata hai.Hacker ko ek clever programmer bhi kaha jata hai kyu ki voh computer ki banayi kadi security ko tod sakta hai.

Mistake 49:Time to time blog ka backup na lena : Blog ka Backup lena bhi bhut jaruri hai, q ki pata nahi kab blog me kuch error aa jaye, ya aapke hath kuch Mistake ho jaye ya Hack ho jaye, to blog ko wapas start karne ke liye pura data to hona hi chaiye, taki blog par kigai mhenat barbad naa jaye. To Chaliye dekhete hai kaise Is Widget ko add kar sakte hai apne blog me.Popular Posts Widget ko Blogger Blog me Add kaise karte haijese ki mene post ke starting me hi kha tha ki ye ek basic jankari hai, Q ki is widget ko add karna bhut aasan hai.. Aap meri steps ko follow kare.Step 1: Blogger.com me Login kare fir apne Blog ke Deshboard me jayeStep 2: ab hame Blogger ke Layout ke section me jana hai.Step 3: layout me aane ke baad, Jaha aapko Popular Posts Widget ko add karna hai wha par Layout me Add a Gadget par click kare.Step 4: Ab ek Popup Window khulegi, jisme bhut se widget ki list hogi jo ham apne blog me add kar sakte hai.. Scroll Down karke Popluar Posts Widget par click kare.Step 5: Ab Popular Posts Widget ki setting ka Page aayega.. Usme aap kesa dikhana chate hai blog me aesi setting kare.Widget ka Title de.. Popular Post Top Post Top News kuch bhi de sakte ho, ya fir khali bhi rakh sakte hai.Konsi Popular Post dikhani hai..Pure Time se jo Popular post hai uske liye All time select kare.Pichle 30 din ki popular post dikhane ke liye Last 30 days select kare.Pichle 7 din ki popular post dikhne ke liye Last 7 days select kare.image thumbnail: agar aap apni post ki image bhi dikhana chate hai to tik karde.snippt: Post ke title ke sath starting ki kuch line bhi dikhana chate hai widget me to isko tik kare.Widget me kitni Popular Post dikhana chate hai wo select kare.Puri setting karne ke baad Save ki button par click karke save karde.AB aap apne blog ko Open karke dekhe Widget dikhne laga hoga or jo aapke blog ki popular post hai wo bhi usme dikhne ladi hogi.

tkai jab koi search kare to google hamari site ko search result me dikhaye. SEO Kitne Prakar ke hote hai ? SEO ka matlab to aap samaj gaye, ki site ko search engine achi se samaj sake uss trha se teyar karna.. par isme bhi bhut si chije aati hai.. par agar ham isko main 2 part me dekhte hai: On Page SEO Off Page SEO #1 On Page SEO On Page SEO kya hai, wo aapko thoda to uske naam se hi samaj aa gaya hoga.. On Page SEO ka matlab hai wo SEO jo hame hamari site ke page par hi karna hai jisse search engine usko samaj sake ki uske kya hai or usko search me dikhaye. On Page SEO kaise karte hai uske ware me detail me har ek point ko bataya huaa hai, aap usko jarur read kare.. q ki agar aapko ON Page SEO kya hai samaj aa gaya or usko kaise karte hai to aapka 60% kaam to bina mhenat ke ho jayega. On Page SEO me kya hota hai: Title Meta description permalink Keyword Internal Link Content length Image optimize Site loading speed Ye sab On Page SEO me aate hai, inka kya matlab hai or kaise inka use hai wo sab aapko SEO Page SEO ki post me mil jayega. #2 Off Page SEO Off Page SEO kya hai wo bhi aap naam se samaj gaye goge, matlab wo SEO jo Page se hatkar karna hai.. Matlab site par jo bhi dalna tha, jo bhi setting karni thi wo sab ON Page SEO me kardi.. khene ka matlab wo sab kuch jisse site search me me aaye or jo site se bhar ho wo Off Page SEO hota hai. Off Page SEO kya hai or wo kaise karte hai uski detail Post bhi aapko HMH.pe mil jayegi, aap On Page SEO ko sikhne ke baad Off Page SEO ko bhi achi se samje. Off Page SEO me kya kya hota hai: Backlink (High Quality Backlink) Social Signal Guest Post Link Exchange Paid Promotion <a title="Web Directory Kya Hai ?

simple aapko isme apni website or page ka URL dalkar check karna hai.bots crawl kar pa rahe ke nahi site ko ?Search engine Bots site ko crawl karte hai uske baad hi site ko search me dikhagaya jata hai, aese me ye bhi ho sakta hai galti se robots.txt se aapne bots ko block kar diya ho or search engine aapki site ko crawl hi nahi kar pa rahe ho.Robot.txt me to koi gadwad nahi hai wo aap Google ke Free Robots Testing Tool me dekh sakte hai.Step 2: Check Google Algorithm UpdatesTraffic achanak loss hone ka ye bhi ek karan ho sakta hai google me koi bada algorithm update kiya ho, uski jankari ke liye online kuch popular blog hai waha dekh sakte hai.Sabse best tarika kisi bhi update ko pata katne ka twitter hai, q ki yaha aapko sabhi top seo mil jayege.Ab Twitter par kisi bhi Update ko dekhne ke liye aap simple search kar sakte hai, google algorithm update jese aap screenshot me dekh sakte hai.Step 3: Google Search Console Check kareGoogle Search console me aapne apni site ko to add kiya hi hoga, agar nahi kiya hai to abhi add kare wo bhut jaruri hai.Jab bhi koi update aata hai or uski baja se site par koi bhi dikkat hoti hai to waha hame error message mil jata hai, or ham unke bataye tarike ko follow karke usko sahi kar sakte hai.Aap Search console me check kare kahi koi error to nahi aa rahi hai aapki site ko crawl karne me, or ye bhi check kare aapki site ki kitni post index hai.Google Search Console important settings karna bhi jaruri hai, agar aapne abhi tak nahi ki to wo bhi jarur kare.Step 4: Google Analytics me Check karewebsite ki traffic kam hone ka karan aap google analytics se bhi laga sakte hai, aap site ka google analytics open karke uska traffic graph dekhe, isse aapko bhut si jankari mil jayegi.Jese example: google ka ek update aaya tha jisme mobile friendly site ko top par dikhate hai, to aese me agar aap google analytics me dekhte to aapki computer ki traffic to same rheti par agar aapki site mobile friendly nai hoti to aapki mobile ki traffic kam hoti.Iss trha ki bhut si chijo ko dekh kar bhi aap google analytics se pata laga sakte hai, akhir traffic kam hone ka karan kya hai.Agar aapne Google analytics add nahi kiya hai to abhi kare, Google Analytics kaise add kare site me uski jankari yaha di hui hai.Step 5: Check Site SpeedWebsite ki speed ek ranking factor hai google me, or agar aapki site ki speed slow hai to ye bhi ek main karan ho sakta hai aapki traffic ka achanak kam hone ka.Website ki speed kaise improve kare uski tips mene share ki hai, unko follow kare uske sath agar kuch bhi aesi chije ho jiske karan aapki site ki speed kam ho rahi hai to unko bhi tikh kare.website ki speed check karne ke liye Googles PageSpeed Insights ka use kar sakte hai, isme kaha kya gadwad hai wo bhi pata chal jati hai.Step 6:Check MobileGoogle ne ye saaf kar diya hai, ki Mobile ke liye phele Mobile friendly site hi dikhai jayegi or unko ko jada value di jayegi, to hamare liye ye bhut jaruri hai ki site mobile me achi trha se open ho.blog Mobile me achi trha se open ho uske liye aap ek badi Mobile Friendly Template use kare.website Mobile Friendly hai ya nahi wo aap Google keMobile-Friendly Test tool ki madad se pata kar sakte hai.Step 7: Backlink Check kareBacklink wo link hoti hai jo kisi dusri site par hamari kisi page ki link add ki gai ho.
Apni Online tutor website ki marketing ke liye aap social networking sites use kar sakte hain.

Whatsapp ke sath sath aap dusre App bhi lock kar sakte hai. Iss App ki ek khas baat or hai wo ye ki aap App ka Icon bhi change kar sakte hai, jisse kisi ko pata hi nahi chalega ki konsa app kaha hai. Lock For Whats Messenger Emojidom Whatsapp me Emojis hai or agar aap whatsapp use karte hai to unka bhi jarur istmal karte hoge.. par agar aap apne whatsapp ke experience ko or badiya emojis se badana chate hai to aap iss ap ka use kar sakte hai. Emojidom CropShop Whatsapp ka use aap karte hai to aapko ye bhi pata hoga ham whatsapp me jo DP (Profile Picture) hai wo sirf square image daal sakte hai, to aese me bhut war hota hai hamari koi achi picture jo square nahi hai usko ham achi se set nahi kar pate.. aese Time par aapCropShop ka use kar sakte hai. CropShop ki madad se Kisi bhi image ko Crop kar sakte hai or usko badi aasani se sqare bana sakte hai. Blogging ke Faide kitne hai wo me phele hi share kar chuka hu, par uske aalawa bhi kuch bate hai jinki [&#8230;] The post Blogging Q Kare Uske 13 Faide [Blogging Benefits] appeared first on Hindi Me Help. Blogging Kya hai or Blogging me Kya hota hai ye Aaj bhut log jante hai par Blogging ke Kya Faide hai or Ham Blogging Q Kare ye baat bhut logo ko clear nahi hai.. Blogging ke Faide kitne hai wo me phele hi share kar chuka hu, par uske aalawa bhi kuch bate hai jinki baja se aapko blogging karni chaiye jo me abhi aapse share kar raha hu. Blogging Q Kare Janiye Uske Benefits #1 Blogging se Paise Kama sakte hai: Agar aap Blogging ke ware me thoda bhut knowledge rakhte hai to aapko pata hi hoga ham Blog bana kar paise kama sakte hai.. Blog se paise kamane ke liye uspar ads lagate hai ya fir Affiliate Marketing se bhi blog ke jariye acha khasa paisa kamaya ja sakta hai. #2 Blogging Aasan hai: Duniya ka wese to koi bhi kaam muskil nahi hai, wass ham jo bhi kaam kar rahe hai us kaam me hame maja aana chaiye, to hame wo muskil lagega hi nahi.. Tikh ussi trha bhut logo ko Blogging me maja aata hai or jinko blogging me maja aata hai unke liye duniya ka sabse aasan kaam ye hi hai, Q ki isko puri Duniya ke kisi bhi kone se kar sakte hai. #3 Popularity: Agar Aapka ek Blog hai or aap usme badiya content dalte hai to kuch time me aapko bhut log phechanne lagege. Ek Trha se aap Dusro ke liye misal hoge q ki bhut logo ko to itna hi jaan kar herani ho jati hai ki inki koi website hai.. Q ki unko ye bhi pata nahi hota Website kaise banaye jo ki bhut aasan hai #4 Blogging hame Acha Insan Banati hai: Jo Log kuch time se blogging kar rahe hai aap unse baat karke dekhna, aapko ek alag hi positivity unke andar mhesus hogi.

All About TrueCallerAgar aapne TrueCaller use kiya hai to aapke mind me bhi ye sabal aaya hoga ki TrueCaller number ki detail lata kaha se hai or ye work kaise karta hai.Truecaller ka kaam karne ka tarika bhut simple hai, wo kisi bhi number ki detail batane ke liye uske database me uss number ko search karta hai.. or jesa ki mene bataya 300+ crore se jada number ki detail truecaller ke pass hai.Truecaller jo number ki detail collect karta hai unke kuch tarike hai, jinki madad se wo pata karte hai ki konsa number kon use kar rahe hai.Social Media: Truecaller number ko Social Media par search karta hai, jese Facebook, Twitter.. agar uss number se koi account hai to wo naam truecaller bata deta hai.TrueCaller App: jo log Truecaller App use karte hai unka uspar account banta hai, iss trha truecaller ke pass unki detail aa jati hai..Contact Book: Truecaller App use karne par wo hamare Phone me save contact ko bhi read kar sakte hai, iss trha hamare phone me jitne bhi number save hai unki detail bhi truecaller ke pass chali jati hai.Direct Submit: Truecaller me direct kisi number ko bhi submit kar sakte hai or uska name suggest kar sakte hai.To ab aapko ye to clear ho gaya hoga ki Truecaller number ki detail lata kaha se hai.. To ab aage se kabhi bhi kisi ko call kare to ye naa soche ki aapka number unke pass save nahi hai to wo pata nahi kar payege ki aap kon ho..Aapka jo Mobile number hai wo aapne Social Media par to use kiya hoga, ya kisi aese user ke mobile me save hoga jo Truecaller use karte hai ya aap khud Truecaller App use karte hai.

MLM company ko to unhone chor diya, par jitne time tak wo usme kaam kar rahe the, usme unhone bhut si chije sikhi, or sambe main baat jab wo MLM kar rahe the to unhone Marketing ki bhut books bhi padhi. Marketing ka unko itna knowledge ho gaya tha ki unhone, Marketing ke upar ek Book bhi likh di, lekin Book bhi ek Failure hi sabit hui. Jo sandeep maheshwari book likhi thi, uski bhi ek khas baat thi, wo ulti open hoti thi matlab piche se or uske sabse phele Page par hi likha tha agar aap apne padhne ka tarika nahi badal sakte, to aap apni soch ko kaise badal sakte ho. Ye jo Book likhi, Marketing ke upar bhale wo success nahi hui, par usko likhne se jo Sandeep Maheshwari ko mila wo sabse badke tha.. Q ki unhone ek book likhne ke chakkar me pata nahi kitni marketing ki book badh dali, jisse unko marketing ka acha khasa knowlage ho gaya. May 26, 201749Facebook Twitter Google+ WhatsApp PinterestHello Bloggers, Aaj ham is Post me dekhege kaise apni Post me Youtube Video ko add karte hai.Me phele hi bata chuka hu ki ham video ko direct post editor sekaise add kar sakte hai, is post me, jisme mene Post editor ke sare option ke bare me batya hai..Sayad aapko pata hi hoga ki ham youtube se bhi badiya paise kama sakte hai, or agar hamara blog bhi hai to usse hamare video ke views to badege hi sath hi sath income bhi badegi.. blog or Youtube dono ki.Start karne ke phele mesamajta hu aapne apna video youtube me upload kar diya hai, or agar aap koior ka video add karna chate hai to wo bhi kar sakte hai.Youtube Video ko add karne ke liye phele hame Youtube Video ka Embed code lena hoga fir ham usko Apne Blog ke HTML me daal kar Video Add kar sakte hai.Youtube Video ka HTML EmbedCode kaise leSabse phele aap jis video ko add karna chate hai usko youtube me khole..Ab niche aap dekhege Share ka Option hai, uspar click kare, Fir Embed par click kareAb ek code aa jayega jisko ham kahi bhi HTML me add karke video ko add kar sakte hai.Agar aap video ko apne hisab se customize karna chate hai to aap SHOW MORE par click kare.Ab kuch or Option aayege, jinko ham apne video me set kar sakte hai.Video Size Aap jo video hai uska kya size rakhna chate hai usko select kar sakte hai.Show Suggested Video isko agar aap Tik karte hai to Video khatam hone ke baad jo Video ka suggestion aate hai wo aayege.Show Player Control Is option me jo Video player ke option hai, Play, Volume , settings wo nahi dikhege.Show Video Title Agar aap Video ka Title dikhana chate hai to isko tik kare.Enable Privacy is option tik karne par youtube hamare visitor ko jab tak track nahi karega jab tk wo video ko play nahi karte.
